{"tid":1281274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"給絕望的死士","createTime":"2019-07-03T08:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T09:07:39.000Z","uid":38737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e85d37c40e225ea74640217af729b1e8366483e","tid":1281274,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"給絕望的死士：<br />\nFor those who are feeling desperate:<br />\n<br />\n只想讓你知道一件事<br />\nWe just want you to know   this:<br />\n<br />\n林奠唔在乎你，我地在乎<br />\n林奠唔聽你，我地繼續一齊講<br />\n林奠唔理你，我地繼續一齊做<br />\nThe government doesn't care, but we do.<br />\nThe government doesn't listen, but we are going to keep speaking up.<br />\nThe government doesn't give a shit, but we are going to make changes.<br />\n<br />\n今朝我地有近千人去搵一個人，就係想你知道，我地會關心身邊既每一個人、我地會緊張身邊既每一個人、我地更愛護身邊既每一個人。<br />\nThis morning nearly a thousand people look for ONE person. We want to let you know we NEED, CARE and LOVE every single one of you.<br />\n<br />\n過去4個人選擇離去，果種心痛比我地自己中催淚彈、布袋彈、胡椒噴霧、捱警棍更痛更痛，入心入肺！呢種痛根本係形容唔到。<br />\nThere were Four people chose to end their life. I am telling you this is more painful than getting hit by tear gas, pepper spray, bean bag round or baton. It is so heartbroken!<br />\n<br />\n我地真係輸唔起！<br />\nWe can't afford to lose one more.<br />\n<br />\n我知道我地做左好多、好多都無咩成果，但我地更加知道，我地身邊有一班為同一個目標，保持初心既人，以行動證明我地 &ndash; 不撤不散。<br />\nI know we haven't achieve anything, but we have each other. We have the same goal.<br />\n<br />\n所以，請繼續同我地一齊並肩奮戰，齊上齊落，同聚同散。<br />\nSo please don't abandon us. We do things together and we are going to win together.<br />\n<br />\n保持希望！！！<br />\nHave faith.<br />\n<br />\n一直與你同行的人<br />\nFrom all of us<br />\n<br />\n#正能量<br />\n<br />\nCredit: tg哨兵channel"},{"pid":"22ffbf2a41ec5e12e7bc70e6b401d6718c015615","tid":1281274,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384b1b75685e77e91d5b08010ce93ca0084bfa3b","tid":1281274,"uid":10726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"我地真係好撚在乎你<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好再做傻事<br />\n<br />\n真係會好撚驚同傷心<br />\n<br />\n聽到嗎?"},{"pid":"a88a3142064442848c2dc16cc1b147fd960a28d1","tid":1281274,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ffbf2a41ec5e12e7bc70e6b401d6718c015615","tid":1281274,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010323a06a8c56556f1515733b9d0dbca03ae87c","tid":1281274,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"邊個再有一絲自殘明志諗法既企出黎 等我屌撚醒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"1121674553884408d4f6d25dac87150676902f18","tid":1281274,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7113861ac5c89af987db4e75c247a07603123b98","tid":1281274,"uid":266677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:56:52.000Z","msg":"一日未成功 一日都唔可以死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e88cd8bd5dd520b8321cc8a611bc63815632d3a","tid":1281274,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[[注意]]！隔離自稱物資店店長個po有問題！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281152</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，打錯&ldquo;&ldquo;站&rdquo;&rdquo;字，見到請幫推"},{"pid":"0ce40df7ca9e8b604de0d2bd9ede2e3e775f0c25","tid":1281274,"uid":253325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"唔係3個咩?"},{"pid":"82b1db94c4c61c4126674546563d30801ddfc1d3","tid":1281274,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:58:02.000Z","msg":"［無名英雄的說話］報道已出街！請記住他們的話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">雲仔都未死 你地做乜要死</span></span>"},{"pid":"b93061b1ce55f00bb79ad2775e59434ef1ea9b7d","tid":1281274,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"每日燒港人港地比烈士睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死唔眼閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45e6c40330a2034cb87265445290ebdc1242ac8","tid":1281274,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"【極緊急】快啲幫手舉呢個仆街 放義士相上網<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281304\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281304</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}